                    <img src="https://www.aeonmall-tanphuceladon.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/dookki-logo.png" alt="Company Logo">
                    <div class="job-details">
                        <h3>Quản Lý Cửa Hàng</h3>
                        <p>Hồ Chí Minh City, Tân Phú | Full Time | <span class="job-salary">$ Thương lượng</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="job-action">
